. Founded in the year 2012, Department of Management Science (COCSIT), has since been a center of learning and development. It has been constantly metamorphosing itself to be at the forefront of the evolutionary academic entity on one side and a skilled human resource provider to the corporate world on the other. The Department of Management Science (COCSIT), Under the Swami Ramanand Teerth Marathwada Open University, is one of the leading Management Institutes in Latur, is a pioneer by itself in the field of Management Studies. The Department of Management Science is a dynamic and forward-thinking academic department committed to creating future leaders, entrepreneurs, and change-makers. Rooted in strong theoretical foundations and real-world application, the department offers innovative programs that equip students with the skills required to thrive in a competitive global business environment. YCMOU has sectioned Study Centre to Department to offer distance learning education through the courses like B. Com, M.Com, and MBA for the students who are working Professional and couldn’t afford to attend regularly. Courses Offered: Regular Mode ❖ BBA (Bachelor of Business Administration) Course Level: Undergraduate Duration: Three or Four years System: 6 or 8 Semesters with multiple entry and exit. The following option will be made available to the students joining BBA Research Program: ◆ One year: Under Graduate Certificate in Business Administration ◆ Two years: Under Graduate Diploma in Business Administration ◆ Three years: Bachelor in Business Administration (BBA) ◆ Four years: Bachelor in Business Administration with Honours: BBA (Honours) ◆ and Bachelor in Business Administration Honours with Research: BBA (Honours with Research) Distance Mode (Yashwantrao Chavan Open University) ❖ B.Com (Bachelor of Commerce) Duration: 3 Years ❖ M.Com (Master of Commerce) Duration: 2 Years ❖ MBA (Master of Business Administration) Duration: 2 Years Infrastructure & Facilities: ►